## How to Test
1. Connect as a **Caissier**.
2. Go to the **Tableau de Bord**.
3. Click on **"Relevé de Compte Détaillé"**.
4. Enter account number `10001234567` (replace with a real one from your DB).
5. Select a date range.
6. Click **Filtrer**.
7. Click **Imprimer** and check the print preview (Ctrl+P).
8. Verify in the database table `journal_audit` that the action was recorded.
